= Common mathematical constants =

The MathConstant class provides a number of static integer values that represent
commonly used constants needed in many mathematical computations.

= M_PI =

Value of PI (~ 3.14159265358979323846...).

= M_PI_2 =

Value of PI / 2.

= M_PI_4 =

Value of PI / 4.

= M_1_PI =

Value of 1 / PI.

= M_2_PI =

Value of 2 / PI.

= M_2_SQRTPI =

Value of 2 / sqrt(PI).

= M_SQRT2 =

Value of sqrt(2).

= M_SQRT1_2 =

Value of 1 / sqrt(2).